snippet: The country’s 45-member United Nations peacekeeping contingent in the Golan Heights was seized by the Syrian branch of Al Qaeda nearly two weeks ago.
abstract: Fiji indicates that its 45-member United Nations peacekeeping contingent in the Golan Heights will be released by Al Nusra Front following nearly two weeks of captivity.
lead_paragraph: The country’s 45-member United Nations peacekeeping contingent in the Golan Heights was seized by the Syrian branch of Al Qaeda nearly two weeks ago.

headline.main: Fiji Government Says Its Golan Heights Peacekeepers Will Be Released Soon
